data.description: Delightful, single level home with a vaulted ceiling, open-concept layout, and thoughtfully designed split bedroom floor plan, exudes a sense of spaciousness and functionality. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, lots of cabinetry, and stainless-steel appliances including a gas range with double ovens. The living room offers a great space for gathering while the Arizona room has the gas fireplace and windows on 3 sides for a bright and airy feel. The master bedroom offers plenty of room with a generous walk-in closet and ensuite bath featuring a walk-in tub and separate shower. Other features of this home include skylights, corner .23 acre homesite and covered front deck entry. Exceptional construction details set this home apart.
